    { h2: "Quick Fixes That Skip the Tow", paras: [
      "A lot of roadside trouble is solvable right where you are. A dead battery needs a jump, not a flatbed. Keys locked in the car need a careful entry, not a wrecker. A flat needs the spare mounted or the car moved to a shop. Roadside assistance covers the everyday problems that strand you without a full tow, and it is usually faster and cheaper than one.",
