      "If it turns out the vehicle needs to move after all, the call rolls straight into <a href='/light-duty-towing-in-grand-prairie/'>light-duty towing</a> or a <a href='/flatbed-towing-in-grand-prairie/'>flatbed</a> for a lowered or non-running car. One call, whichever way it goes.",
